column2: SELECT input.*, po.ra AS sdss_ra, po.dec AS sdss_dec, po.ndetect AS ndetect, pz.z AS photoz, pz.zerr AS photoz_err, po.cmodelmag_u AS cmodmag_u, po.cmodelmagerr_u AS cmoderr_u, po.fibermag_u AS fib3mag_u, po.fiber2mag_u AS fib2mag_u, po.extinction_u AS extinct_u, po.cmodelmag_g AS cmodmag_g, po.cmodelmagerr_g AS cmoderr_g, po.fibermag_g AS fib3mag_g, po.fiber2mag_g AS fib2mag_g, po.extinction_g AS extinct_g, po.cmodelmag_r AS cmodmag_r, po.cmodelmagerr_r AS cmoderr_r, po.fibermag_r AS fib3mag_r, po.fiber2mag_r AS fib2mag_r, po.extinction_r AS extinct_r, po.cmodelmag_i AS cmodmag_i, po.cmodelmagerr_i AS cmoderr_i, po.fibermag_i AS fib3mag_i, po.fiber2mag_i AS fib2mag_i, po.extinction_i AS extinct_i, po.cmodelmag_z AS cmodmag_z, po.cmodelmagerr_z AS cmoderr_z, po.fibermag_z AS fib3mag_z, po.fiber2mag_z AS fib2mag_z, po.extinction_z AS extinct_z, wa.ra AS wise_ra, wa.dec AS wise_dec, wx.match_dist AS wise_dist, wa.w1mpro AS wise_mag_w1, wa.w1sigmpro AS wise_sig_w1, wa.w1snr AS wise_snr_w1, wa.w2mpro AS wise_mag_w2, wa.w2sigmpro AS wise_sig_w2, wa.w2snr AS wise_snr_w2, wa.w3mpro AS wise_mag_w3, wa.w3sigmpro AS wise_sig_w3, wa.w3snr AS wise_snr_w3, wa.w4mpro AS wise_mag_w4, wa.w4sigmpro AS wise_sig_w4, wa.w4snr AS wise_snr_w4, tm.j_m_k2#fe AS tmass_mag_j, tm.j_msig_k2#fe AS tmass_sig_j, tm.h_m_k2#fe AS tmass_mag_h, tm.h_msig_k2#fe AS tmass_sig_h, tm.k_m_k2#fe AS tmass_mag_k, tm.k_msig_k2#fe AS tmass_sig_k, ft.peak AS first_peak, ft.rms AS first_rms FROM MyDB.AKARImain_SDSSspecDR1#_bestobjid input INNER JOIN PhotoObjAll po ON po.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMassXSC tm ON tm.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN FIRST ft ON ft.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN WISE_xmatch wx ON wx.sdss_objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN WISE_allsky wa ON wa.cntr = wx.wise_cntr ORDER BY search_id
